    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >60+个棋子开放，自由组合构筑流派</h2>序章版本我们将开放60多个棋子，正式版有将近150个棋子，包含恶魔、机械、建筑和食物等十多种类型，你可以根据各个棋子之间的组合构筑你的最强军队，击败人类勇者！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179000/extras/18ad74dff5781bd5439dffce28c005de.poster.avif?t=1728667393\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179000/extras/18ad74dff5781bd5439dffce28c005de.webm?t=1728667393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179000/extras/18ad74dff5781bd5439dffce28c005de.mp4?t=1728667393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >数十种棋子合成配方，发挥最强效果</h2>序章版本依旧会保留棋子的合成玩法，兽人步兵+生肉+火精灵能合成兽人厨师，狼+冰精灵能合成霜狼，还有各种奇思妙想的组合等待你的解锁。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179000/extras/8e2ce194d622ce708509975ec3f3757f.poster.avif?t=1728667393\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179000/extras/8e2ce194d622ce708509975ec3f3757f.webm?t=1728667393\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179000/extras/8e2ce194d622ce708509975ec3f3757f.mp4?t=1728667393\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >通关后的额外挑战，更加强力的怪物</h2>游戏攻破敌人城堡后，还可以选择【额外挑战】，利用现有阵容面对更多的敌人以及更坚固的防守，你是否能撑下来呢？！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179000/extras/5918aaadad8c5eaadb43eb9c7bebf2c1.poster.avif?t=1728667393\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179000/extras/5918aaadad8c5eaadb43eb9c7bebf2c1.webm?t=1728667393